<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: #F9F9F9;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #C72C41;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6; /* Improved line spacing for readability */
            margin: 10px 0;
            max-width: 600px; /* Limit width for better reading experience */
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto; /* Center the content */
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            background-color: #C72C41;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #A82333; /* Darker shade on hover */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Your privacy is important to us. We do not share your personal information with third parties without your consent.</p>
    <p>Please review our privacy policy carefully.</p>
    <a href="/user/dashboard">Back to Dashboard</a>
</body>
</html>
